WEBVTT

1
00:00:22.010 --> 00:00:24.930
<b>有许多关于骑士精神的故事
<b>There are many stories of chivalry</b></b>


2
00:00:25.010 --> 00:00:28.350
<b>讲述英勇的骑士救出身陷危险的少女
<b>where the heroic knight saves the damsel in distress.</b></b>


3
00:00:30.010 --> 00:00:33.010
<b>但这个故事不一样
<b>This is not one of them.</b></b>


4
00:01:05.720 --> 00:01:07.100
<b>它在那里
<b>There it is.</b></b>


5
00:01:07.890 --> 00:01:09.350
<b>列阵!
<b>Form up!</b></b>


6
00:01:11.680 --> 00:01:13.430
<b>去干掉这头野兽
<b>Let's kill the beast.</b></b>


7
00:01:13.510 --> 00:01:15.220
<b>为荣耀而战!
<b>For glory! Hyah!</b></b>


8
00:01:30.510 --> 00:01:31.390
<b>保持警惕
<b>Be on guard.</b></b>


9
00:02:12.390 --> 00:02:13.310
<b>排成一行!
<b>Form the line!</b></b>


10
00:02:45.010 --> 00:02:45.850
<b>坚守阵地!
<b>Hold!</b></b>


11
00:03:26.760 --> 00:03:29.810
<b>几个世纪后❫</b>

12
00:03:34.060 --> 00:03:37.010
<b>在遥远的土地上❫</b>

13
00:03:45.430 --> 00:03:46.810
<b>只找到最后一根了
<b>The last I could find.</b></b>


14
00:03:47.390 --> 00:03:49.970
<b>你按父亲的要求 把挂毯拿去镇上了吗?
<b>Did you take the tapestries into town like Father asked?</b></b>


15
00:03:50.060 --> 00:03:50.890
<b>今早去了
<b>This morning.</b></b>


16
00:03:51.470 --> 00:03:54.600
<b>我们应该把皮草和布帘都带去
<b>We should take the furs too, and the drapes.</b></b>


17
00:03:54.680 --> 00:03:55.600
<b>别拿布帘!
<b>Not the drapes!</b></b>


18
00:03:55.680 --> 00:03:57.970
<b>反正你讨厌在房间挂那个图案的布帘
<b>You hate that pattern in your room anyway.</b></b>


19
00:03:58.060 --> 00:03:59.680
<b>布帘是有用的
<b>They serve a purpose.</b></b>


20
00:03:59.760 --> 00:04:02.600
<b>弗洛丽亚 大家都在挨冻
<b>Floria, our people are freezing.</b></b>


21
00:04:02.680 --> 00:04:03.600
<b>饿肚子
<b>And starving.</b></b>


22
00:04:10.430 --> 00:04:11.850
<b>谁会如此深入北境?
<b>Who'd come this far north?</b></b>


23
00:04:20.060 --> 00:04:22.180
<b>伊洛蒂 他们为什么要走?
<b>Elodie, why are they leaving?</b></b>


24
00:04:22.260 --> 00:04:24.390
<b>他们在这一无所有了 弗洛丽亚
<b>There's nothing left for them here, Floria.</b></b>


25
00:04:28.850 --> 00:04:31.060
<b>我还没吃够 拜托 我饿坏了
<b>I don't have enough. Please, I'm hungry.</b></b>


26
00:04:31.140 --> 00:04:32.470
<b>想领食物就排队!
<b>For food, join the line!</b></b>


27
00:04:32.560 --> 00:04:33.430
<b>站到一边
<b>Keep to one side.</b></b>


28
00:04:33.510 --> 00:04:34.600
<b>我要饿死了
<b>I'm starving.</b></b>


29
00:04:35.140 --> 00:04:36.060
<b>那好吧
<b>All right then.</b></b>


30
00:04:37.390 --> 00:04:38.760
<b>松手! 这是我的!
<b>Get off! It's mine!</b></b>


31
00:04:38.850 --> 00:04:41.890
<b>- 嘿! 把食物还给我  - 放开我 老汉!
<b>- Hey! Give me back my food. - Get off of me, old man!</b></b>


32
00:04:41.970 --> 00:04:43.060
<b>你吃得够多了!
<b>You've had enough!</b></b>


33
00:04:43.140 --> 00:04:45.350
<b>跟你姐姐一起吃 去吧
<b>Share this with your sister. Go on.</b></b>


34
00:04:45.430 --> 00:04:47.810
<b>- 你看清是谁了吗?  - 生面孔 小姐
<b>- Could you see who it was? - A stranger, my lady.</b></b>


35
00:04:47.890 --> 00:04:50.140
<b>他们想带走多少木头都可以
<b>They may take whatever wood they can carry.</b></b>


36
00:04:50.220 --> 00:04:51.680
<b>- 遵命  - 来吧 弗洛丽亚
<b>- I'll see to it. - Come on, Flor.</b></b>


37
00:04:51.760 --> 00:04:52.810
<b>- 继续走  - 好
<b>- Move on. - Yes.</b></b>


38
00:04:53.390 --> 00:04:54.720
<b>- 排队  - 快给我
<b>- Get in line. - Give it to me.</b></b>


39
00:04:55.390 --> 00:04:56.510
<b>我想先见见她
<b>I want to meet her first.</b></b>


40
00:04:56.600 --> 00:04:57.720
<b>父亲?
<b>Father?</b></b>


41
00:05:01.930 --> 00:05:03.310
<b>你一定是伊洛蒂
<b>You must be Elodie.</b></b>


42
00:05:03.890 --> 00:05:04.890
<b>没错
<b>I am.</b></b>


43
00:05:18.930 --> 00:05:19.890
<b>她还行
<b>She will do.</b></b>


44
00:05:26.260 --> 00:05:27.430
<b>静候你们的佳音
<b>We await your decision.</b></b>


45
00:05:27.510 --> 00:05:28.680
<b>谢谢 殿下
<b>Thank you, Your Holiness.</b></b>


46
00:05:31.390 --> 00:05:32.390
<b>请走这边
<b>Please, this way.</b></b>


47
00:05:35.560 --> 00:05:37.310
<b>父亲 怎么回事?
<b>Father, what's happening?</b></b>


48
00:05:38.390 --> 00:05:39.350
<b>她是谁?
<b>Who is that?</b></b>


49
00:05:42.220 --> 00:05:43.060
<b>继母?
<b>Stepmother?</b></b>


50
00:05:45.760 --> 00:05:46.810
<b>怎么了嘛?
<b>Well, what is it?</b></b>


51
00:05:47.560 --> 00:05:49.350
<b>来自奥瑞亚女王
<b>From the Queen of Aurea.</b></b>


52
00:05:53.180 --> 00:05:54.180
<b>是来提亲的
<b>A proposal.</b></b>


53
00:05:54.260 --> 00:05:55.390
<b>天哪
<b>Oh, my goodness.</b></b>


54
00:05:57.390 --> 00:05:59.560
<b>- 我帮女儿找到了郎君  - 我看看
<b>- I have made a match. - May I?</b></b>


55
00:06:02.010 --> 00:06:03.100
<b>他是王子
<b>He is a prince.</b></b>


56
00:06:03.930 --> 00:06:04.850
<b>王子?
<b>A prince?</b></b>


57
00:06:06.060 --> 00:06:08.930
<b>我知道你像你母亲一样 一直盼望能出远门
<b>I know you've always wished to travel, as did your mother.</b></b>


58
00:06:09.720 --> 00:06:12.180
<b>去吧 去领略世界
<b>Go. See the world.</b></b>


59
00:06:12.260 --> 00:06:16.350
<b>这个男人拥有一支船队 和装满黄金的马车
<b>This man, he has a fleet of ships, carriages full of gold.</b></b>


60
00:06:16.930 --> 00:06:18.720
<b>这不是结婚的理由
<b>That's no reason to marry.</b></b>


61
00:06:19.890 --> 00:06:21.100
<b>我们要把握机会
<b>We need this.</b></b>


62
00:06:22.140 --> 00:06:23.970
<b>我们的粮仓空了
<b>Our stores are empty.</b></b>


63
00:06:24.060 --> 00:06:26.100
<b>我们熬不到融雪的那一天
<b>We will not make it to the thaw.</b></b>


64
00:06:28.260 --> 00:06:29.640
<b>你的子民需要你
<b>Your people need you.</b></b>


65
00:06:31.350 --> 00:06:32.260
<b>嘿
<b>Hey.</b></b>


66
00:06:34.970 --> 00:06:36.260
<b>这就是我们的职责
<b>This is who we are.</b></b>


67
00:06:48.680 --> 00:06:50.060
<b>过去左舷
<b>Get to the port side.</b></b>


68
00:06:50.680 --> 00:06:51.850
<b>左舷
<b>Port side.</b></b>


69
00:06:57.220 --> 00:06:59.680
<b>伊洛蒂 你怎么了?
<b>Elodie, what's the matter?</b></b>


70
00:07:00.600 --> 00:07:01.600
<b>没什么
<b>Nothing.</b></b>


71
00:07:04.810 --> 00:07:06.470
<b>父亲说 第一次去见
<b>Father says it's natural to be nervous</b></b>


72
00:07:06.560 --> 00:07:08.720
<b>新婚丈夫和他家人 觉得紧张很正常
<b>about meeting your new husband and his family.</b></b>


73
00:07:09.640 --> 00:07:10.850
<b>他们是陌生人
<b>They're strangers.</b></b>


74
00:07:11.430 --> 00:07:15.060
<b>父亲让我措手不及 以前我都没听说过奥瑞亚王国
<b>I've never heard of the Kingdom of Aurea until Father sprang this on me.</b></b>


75
00:07:15.140 --> 00:07:16.310
<b>小心绳索
<b>Mind the lines.</b></b>


76
00:07:18.930 --> 00:07:22.390
<b>你们疯了吗? 你们去那上面做什么?
<b>Are you crazy? What are you two doing up there?</b></b>


77
00:07:22.970 --> 00:07:24.100
<b>快下来
<b>Come down here.</b></b>


78
00:07:25.100 --> 00:07:26.220
<b>来吧
<b>Come on.</b></b>


79
00:07:30.350 --> 00:07:32.890
<b>你就打算这样去见王子吗?
<b>This is how you want your prince to meet you?</b></b>


80
00:07:32.970 --> 00:07:35.010
<b>惶恐不安 浑身冰凉
<b>Scared, cold as a corpse.</b></b>


81
00:07:35.100 --> 00:07:37.260
<b>冻得都流鼻涕了
<b>Nose all drippy and wet.</b></b>


82
00:07:37.350 --> 00:07:40.720
<b>这一路上我是怎么跟你们说的?
<b>What have I been telling you this entire trip?</b></b>


83
00:07:41.220 --> 00:07:42.680
<b>第一印象非常关键
<b>First impressions are everything.</b></b>


84
00:07:43.720 --> 00:07:45.060
<b>来 升起来
<b>Come on, lift up.</b></b>


85
00:07:52.970 --> 00:07:54.180
<b>瞧啊
<b>Look at that.</b></b>


86
00:08:06.720 --> 00:08:08.810
<b>我有好消息 姑娘们
<b>I have good news, girls.</b></b>


87
00:08:08.890 --> 00:08:12.140
<b>船长通知我 我们接近奥瑞亚海岸线了
<b>The captain informs me we approach Aurea's coastline.</b></b>


88
00:08:13.350 --> 00:08:15.140
<b>应该马上就到了
<b>It should be any time now.</b></b>


89
00:08:25.100 --> 00:08:26.350
<b>父亲
<b>Father.</b></b>


90
00:08:29.140 --> 00:08:30.930
<b>什么名堂?
<b>What in the world?</b></b>


91
00:08:33.600 --> 00:08:36.350
<b>好像...好像是...
<b>Looks almost... almost like a--</b></b>


92
00:08:36.430 --> 00:08:37.510
<b>一条龙
<b>A dragon.</b></b>


93
00:09:07.180 --> 00:09:08.350
<b>没事的
<b>It's okay.</b></b>


94
00:09:34.720 --> 00:09:37.930
<b>少女斗恶龙</b>

95
00:09:48.720 --> 00:09:50.890
<b>我的天啊
<b>Oh, my heavens.</b></b>


96
00:10:35.850 --> 00:10:37.010
<b>真是华丽
<b>It's magnificent.</b></b>


97
00:10:37.760 --> 00:10:40.560
<b>大人 夫人 两位小姐
<b>My lords, my ladies,</b></b>


98
00:10:40.640 --> 00:10:43.180
<b>欢迎来到奥瑞亚王国
<b>be welcome to the Kingdom of Aurea.</b></b>


99
00:10:43.720 --> 00:10:46.010
<b>皇室正在祈祷
<b>The royal family is at prayer,</b></b>


100
00:10:46.100 --> 00:10:48.260
<b>但已派人去通报 说各位抵达了
<b>but word has been sent of your arrival.</b></b>


101
00:10:48.350 --> 00:10:51.100
<b>另外 各位的客房均已准备妥当
<b>In the meantime, your rooms have been made ready.</b></b>


102
00:10:51.720 --> 00:10:53.060
<b>请随我来
<b>If you will follow me.</b></b>


103
00:10:55.260 --> 00:10:56.390
<b>这是在做梦吧?
<b>Is this a dream?</b></b>


104
00:10:57.310 --> 00:11:00.350
<b>如果是的话 我能搬进梦乡再也不醒吗?
<b>If so, can I move in and never wake up?</b></b>


105
00:11:01.970 --> 00:11:04.970
<b>如果你想让这些人 认为我们配得上这里
<b>If you want these people to think we belong here,</b></b>


106
00:11:05.060 --> 00:11:08.220
<b>你就不能这么大惊小怪的
<b>you can't act so easily impressed.</b></b>


107
00:11:08.720 --> 00:11:10.060
<b>伊洛蒂 你怎么想?
<b>What do you think, Ellie? Hmm?</b></b>


108
00:11:11.140 --> 00:11:14.140
<b>我觉得这里的富裕程度 远超出我之前的想象
<b>I think I had a rather limited definition of wealthy.</b></b>


109
00:11:35.470 --> 00:11:38.510
<b>我希望这正合您意 小姐
<b>I pray this is to your liking, my lady.</b></b>


110
00:11:39.600 --> 00:11:41.180
<b>浴缸已经备好水
<b>A bath has been drawn</b></b>


111
00:11:41.970 --> 00:11:43.970
<b>膳食也呈上来了
<b>and supper has been carried hence.</b></b>


112
00:11:45.850 --> 00:11:48.640
<b>明天一早 我会来带您去
<b>At first light, I shall return to convey you</b></b>


113
00:11:49.140 --> 00:11:50.720
<b>觐见王子殿下
<b>to meet His Royal Highness.</b></b>


114
00:11:51.310 --> 00:11:53.310
<b>奥瑞亚王子亨利
<b>Henry, Prince of Aurea.</b></b>


115
00:11:55.310 --> 00:11:57.510
<b>弗洛丽亚 别到处乱摸
<b>Floria, stop touching everything.</b></b>


116
00:12:00.640 --> 00:12:01.850
<b>怎么了?
<b>Is something wrong?</b></b>


117
00:12:02.760 --> 00:12:04.640
<b>我只希望他是善良的人
<b>I just hope he's kind.</b></b>


118
00:12:05.390 --> 00:12:06.560
<b>- 知书达理  - 嗯
<b>- And well-read. - Yeah.</b></b>


119
00:12:07.140 --> 00:12:08.140
<b>帅气
<b>Handsome.</b></b>


120
00:12:10.600 --> 00:12:13.390
<b>我们给伊洛蒂留点私人空间吧
<b>Let's all give Elodie some privacy.</b></b>


121
00:12:13.470 --> 00:12:16.760
<b>她可以花点时间适应 我们也一样
<b>She can use the time to settle in, as we all could.</b></b>


122
00:12:16.850 --> 00:12:18.060
<b>确实是呢
<b>Oh, indeed.</b></b>


123
00:12:18.970 --> 00:12:19.930
<b>来吧
<b>Come.</b></b>


124
00:13:15.310 --> 00:13:16.430
<b>小姐
<b>M'lady.</b></b>


125
00:13:17.350 --> 00:13:18.720
<b>大家都在等着了
<b>Everyone's waiting.</b></b>


126
00:14:31.560 --> 00:14:32.560
<b>伊洛蒂?
<b>Ellie?</b></b>


127
00:14:35.220 --> 00:14:36.680
<b>我睡不着
<b>I can't sleep.</b></b>


128
00:14:41.930 --> 00:14:44.430
<b>我依然不敢相信 今后你就要住在这里了
<b>I still can't believe you're going to live here from now on.</b></b>


129
00:14:45.260 --> 00:14:46.470
<b>我也跟你一样
<b>You and me both.</b></b>


130
00:14:47.760 --> 00:14:50.180
<b>我一直在想 要是母亲还在世就好了
<b>I keep thinking, if only Mother were alive,</b></b>


131
00:14:51.260 --> 00:14:53.640
<b>我就能把所有这些事情告诉她
<b>I could just talk to her about all of this.</b></b>


132
00:14:55.350 --> 00:14:57.220
<b>或许你可以跟继母谈谈
<b>Perhaps you could talk to Stepmother.</b></b>


133
00:14:58.140 --> 00:15:01.390
<b>她人很好 虽然她有点...
<b>She means well, even if she is a bit...</b></b>


134
00:15:01.470 --> 00:15:02.600
<b>烦人?
<b>Exhausting?</b></b>


135
00:15:06.390 --> 00:15:09.390
<b>没事的 到时你就知道了
<b>It'll be fine. You'll see.</b></b>


136
00:15:10.810 --> 00:15:13.430
<b>你是伊洛蒂 你无所不能
<b>You're Elodie. You can do anything.</b></b>


137
00:15:16.810 --> 00:15:18.510
<b>你最大的优点是什么?
<b>What is your greatest strength?</b></b>


138
00:15:20.100 --> 00:15:22.060
<b>我从不撒谎 女王陛下
<b>I always tell the truth, Your Majesty.</b></b>


139
00:15:22.760 --> 00:15:25.760
<b>有人会觉得这是弱点
<b>Some might call that a weakness.</b></b>


140
00:15:26.930 --> 00:15:28.220
<b>你了解自己的内心吗?
<b>Do you know your heart?</b></b>


141
00:15:28.970 --> 00:15:30.890
<b>我相信我了解 女王陛下
<b>I believe I do, Your Majesty.</b></b>


142
00:15:31.560 --> 00:15:33.100
<b>你的内心在说什么?
<b>And what is it telling you now?</b></b>


143
00:15:33.180 --> 00:15:37.180
<b>此刻我的心跳得太响 我几乎听不清它在说什么 女王陛下
<b>In truth, it is beating too loudly for me to hear much of anything, Your Majesty.</b></b>


144
00:15:38.220 --> 00:15:39.680
<b>平身吧 伊洛蒂
<b>Arise, Elodie.</b></b>


145
00:15:47.970 --> 00:15:49.060
<b>我是亨利
<b>I'm Henry.</b></b>


146
00:15:50.470 --> 00:15:52.470
<b>很高兴终于见到你了 小姐
<b>Very pleased to finally meet you, my lady.</b></b>


147
00:15:53.470 --> 00:15:54.350
<b>我们都是
<b>We all are.</b></b>


148
00:15:55.760 --> 00:15:58.100
<b>我王儿所言未能表达我们的喜悦心情
<b>My son understates our joy.</b></b>


149
00:15:58.970 --> 00:16:00.180
<b>恕我直言
<b>And if I may say so,</b></b>


150
00:16:00.760 --> 00:16:03.350
<b>你比你父亲说的还要美
<b>your father has understated your beauty.</b></b>


151
00:16:03.930 --> 00:16:07.560
<b>其实我父亲说任何事 一向都言过其实 女王陛下
<b>I've never known my father to understate much of anything, Your Majesty.</b></b>


152
00:16:08.060 --> 00:16:09.720
<b>我看小姐说话还挺风趣
<b>I see she arrives with some wit.</b></b>


153
00:16:09.810 --> 00:16:13.140
<b>她就是这个样子 陛下
<b>Should you want it or not, Your Majesty.</b></b>


154
00:16:13.220 --> 00:16:14.680
<b>你一定是弗洛丽亚
<b>And you must be Floria.</b></b>


155
00:16:16.470 --> 00:16:19.720
<b>看来即便是艰难的环境 也能滋养出最美丽的花朵
<b>It seems even a harsh clime can grow the fairest flowers.</b></b>


156
00:16:19.810 --> 00:16:21.640
<b>我喜欢你们的城堡
<b>I love your castle.</b></b>


157
00:16:21.720 --> 00:16:24.100
<b>我真的很喜欢
<b>I mean, I really love it.</b></b>


158
00:16:24.180 --> 00:16:25.010
<b>非常喜欢...
<b>Like, a lot...</b></b>


159
00:16:27.100 --> 00:16:27.930
<b>女王陛下
<b>Your Majesty.</b></b>


160
00:16:28.510 --> 00:16:30.510
<b>就当这里是自己家就好 孩子
<b>You are to make yourself at home, child.</b></b>


161
00:16:30.600 --> 00:16:35.260
<b>我们几位长辈 有些诸如婚礼等琐事要商量
<b>We elders have some trivial matters like weddings to attend to.</b></b>


162
00:16:35.350 --> 00:16:36.260
<b>是的...
<b>Yes...</b></b>


163
00:16:36.930 --> 00:16:40.350
<b>您在信中提到了有些特别的事宜
<b>Your correspondence made mention of some particulars</b></b>


164
00:16:40.430 --> 00:16:42.470
<b>您希望当面商量
<b>you wish to discuss in person.</b></b>


165
00:16:42.970 --> 00:16:45.390
<b>- 我们二人可以私下商讨  - 好的
<b>- The two of us can confer in private. - Yes.</b></b>


166
00:16:45.470 --> 00:16:47.680
<b>没必要让你们年轻人感到无聊
<b>It's nothing to bore our young people with.</b></b>


167
00:16:48.970 --> 00:16:51.010
<b>他们还有更重要的事要做
<b>They have a far more important task at hand.</b></b>


168
00:16:52.180 --> 00:16:54.010
<b>他们得相互熟悉一下
<b>They must get to know each other.</b></b>


169
00:17:07.180 --> 00:17:08.890
<b>你有什么问题要问我吗?
<b>Do you have any questions of me?</b></b>


170
00:17:10.850 --> 00:17:12.430
<b>关于什么的问题?
<b>Questions of what subject?</b></b>


171
00:17:13.010 --> 00:17:14.510
<b>话题由你选
<b>You may choose the subject.</b></b>


172
00:17:17.390 --> 00:17:18.760
<b>你觉得我怎么样?
<b>What do you think about me?</b></b>


173
00:17:20.260 --> 00:17:21.260
<b>什么?
<b>Pardon?</b></b>


174
00:17:22.390 --> 00:17:25.680
<b>你看起来很不感兴趣 这是你的特权
<b>Well, you seem disinterested at best, which is your prerogative,</b></b>


175
00:17:25.760 --> 00:17:28.470
<b>但是我想知道 我因为内疚而同意的结婚对象
<b>but I'd like to know if the person I'm being guilted into marrying</b></b>


176
00:17:28.560 --> 00:17:29.930
<b>是不是真的喜欢我
<b>truly likes me or not.</b></b>


177
00:17:32.640 --> 00:17:35.600
<b>如果我的态度有所冒犯 我道歉 这不是我的本意
<b>If my attitude offends you, I do apologize. It was not my intent.</b></b>


178
00:17:38.890 --> 00:17:43.810
<b>但是 我并不知道 你是因为内疚才同意这样做的
<b>However, I was unaware that, um, you were being guilted into anything.</b></b>


179
00:17:46.100 --> 00:17:49.970
<b>我的家乡就像你母亲说的一样
<b>The land where I come from is exactly how your mother explained.</b></b>


180
00:17:51.060 --> 00:17:53.180
<b>艰苦而贫瘠
<b>Harsh and barren.</b></b>


181
00:17:54.560 --> 00:17:56.140
<b>这次联姻将会拯救我们的族人
<b>This union will save us.</b></b>


182
00:17:56.220 --> 00:17:57.760
<b>我已经接受了事实
<b>I've made my peace with it.</b></b>


183
00:17:58.640 --> 00:18:02.060
<b>为了我们族人的未来 我个人的幸福只是很小的代价
<b>My happiness is a small price to pay for the future of my people.</b></b>


184
00:18:05.850 --> 00:18:06.810
<b>有什么不对吗?
<b>Is something wrong?</b></b>


185
00:18:09.430 --> 00:18:10.430
<b>只是...
<b>It's just...</b></b>


186
00:18:11.930 --> 00:18:15.560
<b>在你来之前寄的信件里 你的语气不一样
<b>In the letter you sent in advance of your arrival, you sounded different.</b></b>


187
00:18:16.850 --> 00:18:18.600
<b>怎么不一样?
<b>Different. In what way?</b></b>


188
00:18:19.560 --> 00:18:20.680
<b>你在信里更加...
<b>Far more, um...</b></b>


189
00:18:22.850 --> 00:18:23.850
<b>文辞华丽
<b>flowery.</b></b>


190
00:18:25.640 --> 00:18:29.510
<b>或许是因为 大部分内容都是我继母口述的
<b>Maybe that's because my stepmother dictated most of it</b></b>


191
00:18:29.600 --> 00:18:33.010
<b>而那个心是我妹妹的主意
<b>and my sister's idea was the heart...</b></b>


192
00:18:33.720 --> 00:18:34.560
<b>那个心?
<b>The heart.</b></b>


193
00:18:35.600 --> 00:18:38.100
<b>我还以为是某种地方徽章呢
<b>I thought it was some sort of provincial insignia.</b></b>


194
00:18:41.510 --> 00:18:42.760
<b>这真是你画的?
<b>You actually drew this?</b></b>


195
00:18:46.390 --> 00:18:48.140
<b>慢着 这是一个迷宫 对吧?
<b>Hold on. It's a maze, isn't it?</b></b>


196
00:18:48.220 --> 00:18:50.100
<b>"我希望你会了解我的心"
<b>"I hope you'll get to know my heart."</b></b>


197
00:18:50.180 --> 00:18:51.680
<b>真是睿智
<b>That is very clever.</b></b>


198
00:18:53.640 --> 00:18:56.180
<b>弗洛丽亚小时候 我经常给她画
<b>I used to make them for Floria when she was little.</b></b>


199
00:18:57.140 --> 00:18:59.640
<b>- 我能再问你一个问题吗?  - 当然可以
<b>- May I ask you another question? - Certainly.</b></b>


200
00:19:00.510 --> 00:19:02.390
<b>他们总是紧跟着你吗?
<b>Do they always follow you so closely?</b></b>


201
00:19:04.680 --> 00:19:06.260
<b>这已经算是离得远了
<b>This is them giving me space.</b></b>


202
00:19:07.890 --> 00:19:08.930
<b>你肯定觉得心累
<b>That must be tiring.</b></b>


203
00:19:09.930 --> 00:19:11.510
<b>确实是的
<b>It is, actually.</b></b>


204
00:19:13.970 --> 00:19:17.600
<b>我看见马厩里有几匹马无人看管
<b>I saw some horses being left unattended at the stables.</b></b>


205
00:19:21.510 --> 00:19:22.390
<b>你会骑马?
<b>Do you ride?</b></b>


206
00:19:52.350 --> 00:19:55.470
<b>- 你是从哪学会这样骑马的?  - 我母亲教的
<b>- Where did you learn to ride like that? - My mother.</b></b>


207
00:19:56.680 --> 00:19:58.180
<b>现在往哪边走?
<b>Which way now?</b></b>


208
00:19:58.260 --> 00:20:00.350
<b>那就要看你想去看什么了
<b>Well, depends on what you want to see.</b></b>


209
00:20:01.310 --> 00:20:02.310
<b>什么都想看
<b>Everything.</b></b>


210
00:20:03.430 --> 00:20:04.640
<b>好吧
<b>Very well.</b></b>


211
00:20:20.430 --> 00:20:21.810
<b>在里面聊了什么?
<b>What happened in there?</b></b>


212
00:20:24.010 --> 00:20:24.890
<b>快说呀
<b>Speak already.</b></b>


213
00:20:25.810 --> 00:20:28.220
<b>- 还举行婚礼吗?  - 是的
<b>- Is the wedding still on? - Aye.</b></b>


214
00:20:28.930 --> 00:20:31.640
<b>彩礼你谈到好价格了吗?
<b>You settled on a fair bride price?</b></b>


215
00:20:31.720 --> 00:20:34.180
<b>金子多到我无法想象
<b>More gold than I could ever imagine.</b></b>


216
00:20:38.680 --> 00:20:40.350
<b>那你为什么还这副表情?
<b>Then why do you look so?</b></b>


217
00:20:40.430 --> 00:20:42.010
<b>没什么 我没事
<b>No, it's nothing. I'm fine.</b></b>


218
00:20:44.010 --> 00:20:46.560
<b>快告诉我 你没乱说话丢我们的脸吧?
<b>Tell me, you didn't say anything to embarrass us.</b></b>


219
00:20:46.640 --> 00:20:48.100
<b>没有 我没乱说
<b>No, I did not.</b></b>


220
00:20:48.180 --> 00:20:52.010
<b>因为我们两家人必须要和睦相处
<b>Because it's very important that our two families get along.</b></b>


221
00:20:52.100 --> 00:20:54.310
<b>不光是为了伊洛蒂 也是为了我们
<b>Not only for Elodie's sake, but for ours.</b></b>


222
00:20:54.390 --> 00:20:56.930
<b>我说了没事! 没出问题
<b>I said, nothing! Nothing's wrong.</b></b>


223
00:21:00.890 --> 00:21:04.390
<b>我昨天看见高山上有东西
<b>I saw something, high on the mountain last night.</b></b>


224
00:21:05.010 --> 00:21:06.010
<b>有一些火把
<b>Torches.</b></b>


225
00:21:07.930 --> 00:21:09.220
<b>你看到了?
<b>You saw that?</b></b>


226
00:21:09.310 --> 00:21:10.470
<b>我睡不着
<b>I couldn't sleep.</b></b>


227
00:21:12.760 --> 00:21:14.180
<b>那是在举行古老的仪式
<b>It was an ancient ceremony.</b></b>


228
00:21:15.100 --> 00:21:17.060
<b>或者说是三个仪式之一
<b>Or rather, one of three.</b></b>


229
00:21:17.680 --> 00:21:19.600
<b>我们皇室非常重视这种仪式
<b>They're very significant to my family.</b></b>


230
00:21:20.220 --> 00:21:22.310
<b>其实是为了整个王国好 仪式...
<b>For our whole kingdom, really. They, um...</b></b>


231
00:21:23.970 --> 00:21:25.680
<b>是用来向祖先表达敬意的
<b>They honor our ancestors.</b></b>


232
00:21:27.680 --> 00:21:30.390
<b>所以我母亲特意 选了这些日子为我们举办婚礼
<b>That's why my mother chose these dates for our wedding.</b></b>


233
00:21:31.350 --> 00:21:32.760
<b>这太美了
<b>It is quite beautiful.</b></b>


234
00:21:33.680 --> 00:21:34.890
<b>对 我想是的
<b>Yes, I suppose.</b></b>


235
00:21:35.970 --> 00:21:38.470
<b>主要是我没有别的景色跟它做比较
<b>I really don't have anything else to compare it to.</b></b>


236
00:21:39.510 --> 00:21:41.180
<b>我能跟你吐露心声吗?
<b>May I confide in you something?</b></b>


237
00:21:42.140 --> 00:21:43.100
<b>好的
<b>Yes.</b></b>


238
00:21:43.180 --> 00:21:45.850
<b>我最大的愿望是去周游世界
<b>My greatest wish is to go see the world.</b></b>


239
00:21:47.430 --> 00:21:50.640
<b>真的动身去见识一下 你明白吗?
<b>Really set out and see it, you know?</b></b>


240
00:21:51.310 --> 00:21:52.430
<b>其实我明白
<b>I do, actually.</b></b>


241
00:21:53.640 --> 00:21:54.890
<b>这是我一生的梦想
<b>It's my life's dream.</b></b>


242
00:21:57.390 --> 00:22:01.760
<b>从我记事开始 我就渴望去探索遥远的大地
<b>For as long as I can remember, I've longed to explore the distant lands.</b></b>


243
00:22:02.600 --> 00:22:04.260
<b>那些在书里才能看到的地方
<b>The ones you only read about.</b></b>


244
00:22:08.350 --> 00:22:10.220
<b>或许有一天我们可以一起去
<b>Perhaps, one day, we will.</b></b>


245
00:22:12.260 --> 00:22:13.350
<b>或许吧
<b>Perhaps.</b></b>


246
00:22:27.430 --> 00:22:29.510
<b>这一片区域是橙色的
<b>And the orange in this area.</b></b>


247
00:22:33.180 --> 00:22:36.060
<b>一切都很美 女王陛下
<b>Everything's so beautiful, Your Majesty.</b></b>


248
00:22:36.140 --> 00:22:37.720
<b>我很高兴能合你意
<b>Well, I'm glad you approve.</b></b>


249
00:22:38.810 --> 00:22:40.180
<b>很高雅
<b>Very elegant.</b></b>


250
00:22:42.600 --> 00:22:44.810
<b>您的品位真是无可挑剔
<b>You have impeccable taste.</b></b>


251
00:22:45.810 --> 00:22:49.390
<b>所有东西都很精致
<b>Everything is just so exquisite.</b></b>


252
00:22:49.470 --> 00:22:52.220
<b>抱歉 有什么需要帮忙的吗?
<b>I'm sorry, is there something I can help you with?</b></b>


253
00:22:52.890 --> 00:22:55.810
<b>我想着我们或许可以熟络一点
<b>I just thought we might become better acquainted,</b></b>


254
00:22:56.510 --> 00:22:58.760
<b>眼看我们就要成为一家人了
<b>seeing as we're about to be family.</b></b>


255
00:22:58.850 --> 00:23:02.390
<b>这桩婚事肯定令你非常激动
<b>Ah, this must be very exciting for you.</b></b>


256
00:23:02.470 --> 00:23:05.470
<b>你的父亲是绳索匠 对吧?
<b>Your father was a rope maker, was he not?</b></b>


257
00:23:05.560 --> 00:23:07.260
<b>是城里最好的
<b>The finest in the city.</b></b>


258
00:23:07.350 --> 00:23:10.010
<b>现在你们来了这里 爬到了这么高的位置
<b>And here you are. You've climbed so high.</b></b>


259
00:23:11.100 --> 00:23:14.060
<b>即便如此 人还是不能忘了自己的位置
<b>Still, one mustn't forget one's station.</b></b>


260
00:23:14.970 --> 00:23:16.930
<b>也不要过分看重这桩婚事
<b>Nor place undue import</b></b>


261
00:23:17.010 --> 00:23:20.760
<b>毕竟只是一场利益交换而已
<b>on what is ultimately a transaction born of necessity.</b></b>


262
00:23:23.220 --> 00:23:24.060
<b>"利益"?
<b>"Necessity"?</b></b>


263
00:23:24.640 --> 00:23:26.260
<b>你的家庭需要钱
<b>Well, your family needs money.</b></b>


264
00:23:26.930 --> 00:23:28.510
<b>而我们皇室需要新娘
<b>My family needs a bride.</b></b>


265
00:23:29.220 --> 00:23:31.850
<b>我们最不需要的就是再来一群亲戚
<b>What we don't need is more family.</b></b>


266
00:23:33.350 --> 00:23:35.640
<b>我希望亨利和埃洛伊丝百年好合
<b>I wish all the best for Henry and Eloise.</b></b>


267
00:23:35.720 --> 00:23:37.060
<b>- 我只是...  - 伊洛蒂
<b>- I merely-- - Elodie.</b></b>


268
00:23:37.560 --> 00:23:38.390
<b>什么?
<b>Pardon?</b></b>


269
00:23:40.350 --> 00:23:43.470
<b>我的继女 她叫伊洛蒂
<b>My stepdaughter. Her name is Elodie.</b></b>


270
00:23:44.970 --> 00:23:46.060
<b>我就是这么说的
<b>That's what I said.</b></b>


271
00:23:47.010 --> 00:23:48.350
<b>祝你日安 百福特夫人
<b>Good day, Lady Bayford.</b></b>


272
00:24:05.470 --> 00:24:06.310
<b>真是完美
<b>It's perfect.</b></b>


273
00:24:07.220 --> 00:24:08.890
<b>这里的一切都很完美
<b>Everything in here is so perfect.</b></b>


274
00:24:13.180 --> 00:24:14.180
<b>继母
<b>Stepmother.</b></b>


275
00:24:15.930 --> 00:24:17.310
<b>有什么事吗?
<b>Is something the matter?</b></b>


276
00:24:18.760 --> 00:24:19.720
<b>伊洛蒂
<b>Elodie,</b></b>


277
00:24:20.810 --> 00:24:23.100
<b>我知道我们一直以来不算亲密
<b>I know we haven't always been close,</b></b>


278
00:24:23.810 --> 00:24:25.850
<b>但是现在你要听我说
<b>but I need you to listen to me now.</b></b>


279
00:24:26.600 --> 00:24:29.680
<b>这场婚礼...不该办
<b>This wedding... is a mistake.</b></b>


280
00:24:29.760 --> 00:24:30.760
<b>什么?
<b>What?</b></b>


281
00:24:33.180 --> 00:24:34.510
<b>我没听明白
<b>I don't understand.</b></b>


282
00:24:34.600 --> 00:24:37.010
<b>我不信任这些人
<b>These people, I don't trust them.</b></b>


283
00:24:37.600 --> 00:24:41.100
<b>这种感觉很难解释 但是当妈的就是感觉得到
<b>It's hard to explain, but a mother knows these things.</b></b>


284
00:24:41.180 --> 00:24:43.310
<b>昨天你还被这个地方迷住了呢
<b>Only yesterday, you were enamored by this place.</b></b>


285
00:24:43.390 --> 00:24:44.350
<b>弗洛丽亚
<b>Floria.</b></b>


286
00:24:44.430 --> 00:24:45.470
<b>是我搞错了
<b>I was wrong.</b></b>


287
00:24:46.680 --> 00:24:50.810
<b>虽然他们是皇室 但这不代表他们就是好人
<b>They may be royalty, but that doesn't make them good people.</b></b>


288
00:24:52.510 --> 00:24:53.640
<b>嗯...
<b>Well...</b></b>


289
00:24:54.180 --> 00:24:57.260
<b>- 父亲怎么想?  - 他不愿意多说
<b>- What does Father think? - He refuses to talk about it.</b></b>


290
00:24:57.350 --> 00:25:01.510
<b>我试图跟他说我的担忧时 他还斥责我
<b>And when I try to tell him my worries, he snaps at me.</b></b>


291
00:25:01.600 --> 00:25:04.310
<b>- 因为你不讲理  - 够了 弗洛丽亚
<b>- Because you're being unreasonable. - That's enough, Flor.</b></b>


292
00:25:04.890 --> 00:25:10.060
<b>伊洛蒂 我发誓我只想为你好
<b>Elodie, I swear that I only want what's best for you.</b></b>


293
00:25:15.350 --> 00:25:17.060
<b>我是不是打扰你们了?
<b>Am I interrupting something?</b></b>


294
00:25:18.760 --> 00:25:19.810
<b>没有
<b>No.</b></b>


295
00:25:20.720 --> 00:25:21.560
<b>只是...
<b>Just...</b></b>


