01:27:53.850 --> 01:27:57.060
<b>但你并没有做到 我们不是他们的女儿
<b>Except you haven't. We are not their daughters.</b></b>


616
01:27:57.140 --> 01:27:58.810
<b>还撒谎
<b>More lies.</b></b>


617
01:28:36.560 --> 01:28:37.680
<b>伊洛蒂!
<b>Ellie!</b></b>


618
01:28:52.100 --> 01:28:56.850
<b>现在 你就要知道我女儿们的痛苦了
<b>Now, you will know my daughters' pain.</b></b>


619
01:29:44.310 --> 01:29:46.560
<b>我跟他们不是一伙的!
<b>I am not one of them!</b></b>


620
01:29:51.680 --> 01:29:53.970
<b>我闻到了你血液里的气味
<b>I smell it in your blood.</b></b>


621
01:31:19.890 --> 01:31:23.470
<b>伊洛蒂
<b>El-o-die.</b></b>


622
01:31:25.720 --> 01:31:28.100
<b>接受你的命运吧...
<b>Accept your fate...</b></b>


623
01:31:34.060 --> 01:31:36.060
<b>就像我接受命运一样
<b>as I have mine.</b></b>


624
01:31:40.140 --> 01:31:43.760
<b>我们都要孤独死去
<b>We are to die alone.</b></b>


625
01:31:51.100 --> 01:31:52.390
<b>不
<b>No.</b></b>


626
01:31:55.970 --> 01:31:57.930
<b>我身边有一支军队
<b>I have an army with me.</b></b>


627
01:32:00.600 --> 01:32:04.470
<b>在这下面被夺走生命的每个无辜女人
<b>Every innocent woman whose life was stolen down here.</b></b>


628
01:32:06.760 --> 01:32:11.010
<b>你们的族类绝不无辜
<b>Your kind were never innocent.</b></b>


629
01:32:18.180 --> 01:32:19.430
<b>那就来吧
<b>Then go ahead.</b></b>


630
01:32:23.640 --> 01:32:25.260
<b>释放你的烈焰
<b>Show me your fire.</b></b>


631
01:32:30.180 --> 01:32:31.010
<b>怎么?
<b>Well?</b></b>


632
01:32:32.350 --> 01:32:33.810
<b>你还在等什么?
<b>What are you waiting for?</b></b>


633
01:32:36.930 --> 01:32:38.010
<b>喷火烧我吧
<b>Burn me.</b></b>


634
01:32:40.640 --> 01:32:41.680
<b>喷火烧我呀!
<b>Burn me!</b></b>


635
01:33:45.640 --> 01:33:47.260
<b>我的妹妹也有这个
<b>My sister had this too.</b></b>


636
01:33:48.680 --> 01:33:49.810
<b>我们都有
<b>All of us did.</b></b>


637
01:33:50.810 --> 01:33:52.930
<b>他们用这个方法 让我们成为皇室成员
<b>That is how they make us royal.</b></b>


638
01:33:54.310 --> 01:33:56.510
<b>这就是你闻到的血腥味
<b>That is the blood you smell.</b></b>


639
01:34:07.010 --> 01:34:08.180
<b>他们欺骗了你
<b>They fooled you.</b></b>


640
01:34:10.180 --> 01:34:13.510
<b>你一直在残杀无辜的女儿 就像皇室残杀幼龙一样
<b>You've been killing innocent daughters just like they did.</b></b>


641
01:34:21.600 --> 01:34:24.600
<b>那就来个了结吧
<b>Then, end it.</b></b>


642
01:34:51.100 --> 01:34:51.930
<b>不
<b>No.</b></b>


643
01:34:56.810 --> 01:34:59.060
<b>我再也不想听命于别人了
<b>I'm through doing what I'm told.</b></b>


644
01:36:19.100 --> 01:36:19.930
<b>伊洛蒂
<b>Elodie.</b></b>


645
01:36:26.760 --> 01:36:29.600
<b>你得相信我 在那之后 我片刻都睡不着...
<b>You must believe me. I haven't slept a moment since--</b></b>


646
01:36:29.680 --> 01:36:31.510
<b>在你试图杀死我妹妹之后?
<b>Since you tried to kill my sister?</b></b>


647
01:36:33.100 --> 01:36:34.010
<b>我别无选择
<b>I had no choice.</b></b>


648
01:36:34.100 --> 01:36:37.060
<b>不准你向这个平民...
<b>Don't you dare explain yourself to this...</b></b>


649
01:36:37.140 --> 01:36:38.720
<b>多做解释
<b>this commoner.</b></b>


650
01:36:42.970 --> 01:36:44.640
<b>她是要当第三个吗?
<b>Is she to be the third?</b></b>


651
01:36:45.600 --> 01:36:47.100
<b>三号王妃
<b>Princess number three.</b></b>


652
01:36:48.850 --> 01:36:52.310
<b>她是最后一个了 然后我就可以自由迎娶任何...
<b>She's the last, and then I'll be free to marry whoever I--</b></b>


653
01:36:52.390 --> 01:36:54.060
<b>别说了 亨利
<b>That's enough, Henry.</b></b>


654
01:36:55.010 --> 01:36:57.430
<b>你对我们忍受的痛苦一无所知
<b>You know nothing of what we've endured.</b></b>


655
01:36:58.100 --> 01:37:00.350
<b>你完全不了解我们的故事
<b>You know nothing of our story.</b></b>


656
01:37:08.680 --> 01:37:10.060
<b>带上你的家人
<b>Take your family</b></b>


657
01:37:11.890 --> 01:37:13.220
<b>然后跑吧
<b>and run.</b></b>


658
01:37:15.260 --> 01:37:16.600
<b>来 我们走
<b>Come. Let's go.</b></b>


659
01:37:18.430 --> 01:37:21.890
<b>我给你们最后一次逃走的机会
<b>I will offer you all one last chance to do the same.</b></b>


660
01:37:29.390 --> 01:37:30.220
<b>不走?
<b>No?</b></b>


661
01:37:32.310 --> 01:37:34.810
<b>你这个傲慢的东西
<b>You insolent creature.</b></b>


662
01:37:35.850 --> 01:37:37.600
<b>你以为我们现在应该怕你吗?
<b>You think we ought to fear you now?</b></b>


663
01:37:39.010 --> 01:37:39.850
<b>为什么?
<b>Why?</b></b>


664
01:37:40.600 --> 01:37:43.810
<b>因为你设法逃过了恶龙的魔爪?
<b>Because you somehow managed to escape the dragon?</b></b>


665
01:37:47.600 --> 01:37:49.760
<b>你们应该害怕的不是我
<b>It's not me you should fear.</b></b>


666
01:37:51.010 --> 01:37:54.350
<b>你们的故事至此就要终结了
<b>This is the end of your story.</b></b>


667
01:37:55.430 --> 01:37:56.430
<b>快跑!
<b>Run!</b></b>


668
01:38:10.810 --> 01:38:13.470
<b>- 恶龙来了!  - 跑!
<b>- It's the dragon! - Run!</b></b>


669
01:38:36.180 --> 01:38:42.890
<b>不!
<b>No!</b></b>


670
01:39:29.010 --> 01:39:31.180
<b>谁来帮我搬这个桶
<b>Someone give me a hand with this barrel.</b></b>


671
01:39:31.260 --> 01:39:32.930
<b>都放聪明一点 伙计们
<b>Let's be sharp there, lads.</b></b>


672
01:39:33.010 --> 01:39:35.180
<b>开玩笑的吧?
<b>You can't be serious.</b></b>


673
01:39:35.260 --> 01:39:36.140
<b>我没开玩笑
<b>But I am.</b></b>


674
01:39:36.220 --> 01:39:37.970
<b>我们一起经营它
<b>We'll run it together.</b></b>


675
01:39:38.060 --> 01:39:39.640
<b>我们有丰富的物资供应
<b>We've got a bounty of supplies.</b></b>


676
01:39:39.720 --> 01:39:42.100
<b>足以让我们度过这次和下一个寒冬
<b>Enough to get us through this freeze and the next.</b></b>


677
01:39:42.180 --> 01:39:43.220
<b>哦 伊洛蒂
<b>Oh, Elodie.</b></b>


678
01:39:43.310 --> 01:39:46.510
<b>我只信赖你能照看好 我们的子民 母亲
<b>You're the only person I trust to look after our people, Mother.</b></b>


679
01:39:55.390 --> 01:39:56.560
<b>我也能帮忙吗?
<b>Can I help too?</b></b>


680
01:39:59.850 --> 01:40:00.680
<b>弗洛丽亚
<b>Floria.</b></b>


681
01:40:01.220 --> 01:40:02.850
<b>我也指望你啦
<b>I'm counting on it.</b></b>


682
01:40:12.060 --> 01:40:14.600
<b>继母 你快来看看这个
<b>Stepmother. Stepmother, come and see this.</b></b>


683
01:40:14.680 --> 01:40:16.260
<b>天哪
<b>Oh, wide heavens!</b></b>


684
01:40:16.350 --> 01:40:19.510
<b>小姐 我们要去哪?
<b>My lady, what course shall we steer?</b></b>


685
01:40:21.810 --> 01:40:22.810
<b>回家
<b>Home.</b></b>


686
01:47:11.260 --> 01:47:16.260
<b>翻译:杨宇航</b>